data.description: You'll take a DOUBLE TAKE looking at this transformation in South Lake Charles! The exterior now shines with fresh paint, tasteful window shutters, and a welcoming front door, enhancing its already appealing curb appeal.  Inside, a harmonious blend of warmth and functionality awaits. The spacious living room, with its vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace, invites relaxation. Adjacent lies a kitchen fit for a chef, with custom-stained cabinets and a convenient island bar. From here, the dining area opens up to a cozy covered patio—perfect for those weekend brunches or evening wind-downs. The main suite is a retreat, complete with an updated bathroom featuring double vanities, a soaking tub, and a sizable walk-in closet. The guest bedrooms are equally spacious, ensuring comfort for all. Recent upgrades aren't just cosmetic; fresh laminate flooring, foam insulation, a new roof in 2021, and an updated HVAC from 2019 guarantee efficiency. The home also offers a 2-car garage, climate-controlled storage, and a reliable security system.  The backyard, surrounded by a privacy fence, is an ideal spot for barbecues or simply enjoying a sunny afternoon. And for added peace of mind, the flood insurance is a manageable $211/month.  Located in the heart of South Lake Charles, this rejuvenated home is a testament to tasteful modern living. Come see the transformation for yourself!
